# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Viventi — credentials template
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#  WHAT THIS FILE IS:
#  A blank template. It holds NO real key, so it's safe to keep in
#  the project and share. The real key goes in a separate file.
#
#  HOW TO USE IT:
#  1. Make a copy of this file, in the same folder.
#  2. Name the copy exactly  .env  (a dot, then "env" — no ".example").
#  3. In that new .env file, replace the placeholder text after the
#     "=" sign with your real MercadoPago secret key.
#  4. Save it. NEVER share or upload the .env file — it stays private.
#
#  (Not sure how? Ask Claude — it can do these steps for you.)
#
#  WHERE TO GET THE KEY:
#  https://mercadopago.com.mx/developers/panel/credentials
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Secret key — used by the payment handler to charge cards.
# This is the only true secret. Keep it private; never share it.
MP_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token_here

# NOTE: The MercadoPago PUBLIC key is not stored here. It's safe to
# expose and lives directly in index.html (search for MP_PUBLIC_KEY).
